Kalidasa, a government school teacher, is a hard worker who is ridiculed due to his poor English skills. On the personal front, his upper-class wife is unhappy with his social status. When the school faces the threat of being shut down, Kalidasa takes it on himself to fight the education system.

The film tells the story of Bala (Ayushmann Khurana) a man who is balding prematurely and how he copes with the situation. The film also narrates Bala's relationship with two women played by Yami Gautam and Bhumi Pednekar respectively.

Academy Award-winners Matt Damon and Christian Bale star in FORD v FERRARI, based on the remarkable true story of the visionary American car designer Carroll Shelby (Damon) and the fearless British-born driver Ken Miles (Bale), who together battled corporate interference, the laws of physics, and their own personal demons to build a revolutionary race car for Ford Motor Company and take on the dominating race cars of Enzo Ferrari at the 24 Hours of Le Mans in France in 1966.

A group of tourists from India set out on a vacation only to have the trip turn into a patriotic mission. Can they pull it off?

A disguised man gains entry into a joint family and then absconds by kidnapping one of its members, who is also the titleholder of the family's possessions. What follows is a chain of misconceptions that create tension in the family.
An ordinary suburban girl suddenly disappears, leaving her loved ones in a desperate search as she must face the ultimate battle - the one for her life.
Adithya Varma, a short tempered house surgeon, gets into a self destructive phase of drug and alcohol addiction when his girlfriend is forced to marry another person.

George Reddy is a biopic of a student leader, boxer and gold medallist who influenced Andhra Pradesh politics in Osmania University between 1962 and 1972. He inspired revolutionary thoughts until he was brutally murdered at his hostel in 1972.

Shravana wants to sell his house, Shravana Nivasa, but theres a hitch - the house is haunted. He gets Raghupathi, Raghava, Raja and Ram to take up the job of removing the ghost. What follows is a series of hilarious incidents as they deal with the task at hand.
Marjaavaan is a story of love birds Raghu and Zoya enjoying their lives until a vertically challenged gang leader with harmful intentions turns their world upside down.

A Ph.D. researcher returns from London to search for his missing girlfriend. Little does he know that there exists a conspiracy much bigger than he calculated. What follows is a roller coaster ride of emotions, suspense, thrill and drama in this quest of a dedicated lover.
Bhaskaran is a simple man living in a small, conservative village with his son, Subrahmanyan. Both of their lives take a turn for the better when a robot enters their world.

A group of cops confiscate a record amount of drugs but find themselves in danger of the mafia. The injured inspector then takes the help of a life term prisoner, who is out on parole to meet his daughter. Will he be able to save the day?
The film revolves around a father and son duo, a gangster and a football player respectively, who get involved in coaching the womens football team.

Two cop killers are on the loose and a citywide manhunt is on for the criminals. In the middle of the mayhem is a diligent NYPD detective, who is determined to track them down at all costs. As all of Manhattan's 21 bridges are shut down and the situation spirals out of control, he soon becomes unsure of who to pursue - and who is in pursuit of him.

Vidya is happily married to Rahul until tragedy strikes with her husband's death - and she is the one responsible. She becomes the prime suspect during the investigation headed by ACP Narasimha. With growing suspicion and an unending maze of mystery, a secret is revealed which turns everyone's lives upside down.

When 6 lovers are parted because of conspiracy and revenge in the year 1419, the characters cross paths again in 2019. However, in the present life the 3 boys are about to marry their sisters-in-law and the pairings are in the wrong order. Destiny repeats itself when the 3 couples who are choosing their wedding destination all land up in Sitamgarh again, where it all began. Will they remember their past lives in time for marriage or will they be stuck with the wrong lovers forever? Housefull 4 is coming to confuse you, put you on a laughing riot and take you through the grandeur of 1419 with a spark of 2019. Come & witness this Epic Reincarnation Comedy.

Kannad Gothilla is a psychological thriller that follows the story of a senior crime inspector who is assigned to the case of non-Kannadigas going missing in Bengaluru. Will she get to the bottom of the mystery?

Arthur Fleck, a man struggling with loneliness and isolation, wears two masks. One, he paints on for his day job as a clown. The other is a guise he projects in an attempt to find his place in Gotham City's fractured society. Caught in a cyclical existence between apathy and cruelty, Arthur begins to make one bad decision after another. What follows is a new take on the origin story of one of cinema's most iconic villains.

Set in 1975 in a small village in the Rann of Kutch, Gujarat, the social drama centers around the distraught lives of women in a highly patriarchal society. One day, while on their way to fetch water, they find someone in the middle of the desert who creates a dramatic change in their lives.

The title Tholubommalata means life is like a puppet show, which forms the basis of this movie. In a village, an old man named Somaraju lives happily by selling Goli Soda. How he tries to resolve the issues and complexities arising in and around his family and how he behaves as a loving father and grandfather, form the story of this movie that focuses on humans relations versus greed.

The story begins with three teenagers causing an accident at midnight. At the same time, news of a gunshot at a park is reported to the nearby police station where Inspector Ravichandran begins the investigation. The case takes him through many twists and turns but ends up becoming one of the most special cases of his life.

The second installment of the epic fantasy adventure follows the ascendant princess Aurora and the darkly charismatic Maleficent as they try to navigate the complex dynamics between them, form new alliances and confront new adversaries - all in a bid to protect their land and its subjects.

War is a high-intensity Bollywood action drama which stars Hrithik Roshan, Tiger Shroff, Vaani Kapoor, among other stars. Directed by Siddharth Anand, War movie is about a special agent Kabir (Hrithik Roshan) who has gone rogue and his student, Khalid (Tiger Shroff) is entrusted to take him down. Vaani Kapoor plays a pivotal role in this epic battle of teacher vs student. Will Khalid be able to stop Kabir? What made Kabir go rogue and betray his own country? Find out in War, the latest action movie hitting theatres in October 2019. Book your tickets now to witness this thriller, 'War'. Releasing in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu in theatres near you!

A group of college friends plan their reunion in the dense forests of Western Ghats, where they hope to unwind in the grandeur of nature. As they journey to the fabled Karadi Guhe (Bear's Cave) inside the forest, they bond over old memories and share their dreams for the future.

But things take a dark turn when these friends lose their way in the cave, which has all the trappings of a strange labyrinth. A new age psychological suspense thriller, Manaroopa captures the predicament of millennials in a virgin forest as they explore their feelings in an unexplored territory.

Bharaate is a Kannada movie starring Sri Murali and Sree Leela in the lead roles. The film is a romantic family entertainer, consisting of nine villains including roles played by Ravishankar, Saikumar and Ayyappa. It is directed by Chethan Kumar and produced by Supreeth. Arjun Janya has composed the music for the film.
When a systems engineer blows the whistle on a dangerous technology, Charlie's Angels from across the globe are called into action, putting their lives on the line to protect society.

Nirmali, a married Pediatrician in her late 30s, leads a peaceful but joyless domestic existence in Guwahati, Assam. Her husband, a doctor, spends most of his time doing relief work. One day, she meets Sumon, a young PhD student who believes that theres no kind of food that can be considered abnormal. Nirmali is drawn to this idea and the two start bonding over meals comprising of unusual meats, but soon their relationship takes a dark and bizarre turn.

Kiss tells the love story of Nandini and Arjun. Nandini is a young, modern day college student who holds on to traditional values and Arjun is a rich, carefree guy. The film is an exploration of young love, directed by A. P. Arjun and produced by V. Ravi Kumar under Rashtrakuta Pictures. The lead actors are Viraat Vellanki and Sree Leela. The credit for the music score goes to V. Harikrishna and Adi Hari.

Teenager Yi is taken by surprise when she encounters a Yeti on the roof of her apartment and along with her friends Jin and Peng, decide to name him "Everest". Together they embark on a quest to reunite Everest with his family and begin their journey to the highest point on Earth.

The only obstacle in their path is Burnish, a wealthy man who is intent on capturing a Yeti and the zoologist Dr. Zara.

Motichoor Chaknachoor revolves around a young, small town girl who wants to get married as a means to settle abroad, and a 36 year old man who is looking for a wife. When the two finally meet, will sparks fly? Will she get the flight she wants?

Jack, a thief who hoodwinks the system and steals black money, is chased by Daniel, a cop intent on catching him. This action thriller portrays a game of cat and mouse that will keep you on tenterhooks!

Karuppu Durai, an 80-year-old man, bedridden for the past three months in a coma, suddenly wakes up one fine day to overhear his family planning to kill him by performing an ancient euthanasia ritual. Hurt, heartbroken and afraid, Karuppu Durai runs away from the only home he has ever known. On an aimless path with nowhere to go, he accidentally meets a 10-year-old orphan Kutty. Kutty is everything Karuppu Durai isn't; smart, spunky and full of life. The fiercely independent Kutty encourages KD to chalk out a bucket list and start living for himself. Thus begins an eventful road trip of this unlikely pair - an old man running away from his family and a young boy who never had one!
Gani is an unemployed youth who has a dream to start his own business, but luck doesn't work in his favor. This romantic comedy is a laugh riot that will leave you in stitches.

Two estranged brothers who have been driven apart by circumstances and life choices are reunited by a strange twist of fate. What follows forms the crux of the story in this yesteryear classic starring Sandalwood icon Rajkumar
Set against a rural backdrop, Sangathamizhan revolves around a farmer who gets involved in politics and ends up going against the biggest politician in town.
Khaidi revolves around a convict serving a life sentence who escapes from prison but ends up being chased by more than just the police.

Rollercoaster - A crazy ride on a long and thrilling rollercoaster amidst creatures from sea and dinosaurs.

Alien Visits Ancient Earth - An alien lands on Earth, millions of years ago by mistake, but enjoys exploring the world with huge dinosaurs, ants and multi-headed monsters which roam around.
A regular college student Raghu gets dragged into chaos when he falls in love with Lekha. What starts as a whirlwind romance pulls Raghu into controversies that change the course of his life.
Colonel Subhash, an Indian army officer, is on a mission to catch a mastermind behind a terror attack that took away some of his loved ones.

Jungle Adventure and Desert Coaster is an English, 7D, virtual reality show, which will take you on the adventure of a lifetime! Get ready to leave reality behind and dive into an exciting and thrilling journey.

A commercial tale with an all children cast, Girmit is a one of a kind movie. This family drama portrays Ashlesh Raj as Raj and Shlagha Saligrama as Rashmi, the lead characters. The film is directed by Ravi Basrur and produced by N S Raj Kumar.
Film portrays an incredible true story of indomitable human spirit, based on the 26/11 terrorist attacks at the Taj Mahal Palace Hotel, Mumbai in 2008.

Rajalakshmi is a Kannada movie starring Naveen, Rashmi and Honnavalli Krishna in prominent roles. It is a drama directed by Kantharaj Gowda with A. T. Raveesh as musician, forming part of the crew.

Four people are on a killing spree in a remote village. Their prime targets are the single ladies of the village. When they kidnap a girl, however, the man who is in love with her decides to go after them and is willing to go to any heights to save her.

Alex tells the story of a boy and a girl who live very different lives but are brought together by fate. This accidental meeting leads the two strangers to become the entire world for each other, taking them on the journey of a lifetime!

Andavaada follows a young man's quest to find the true love of his life. Directed by Chala, the film stars Jai and Anusha in the lead roles.

An intense and relatable high school drama set in Bangalore in the 1990s, Gantumoote is the tale of a sixteen-year-old girl and her subtle journey from the life that she thinks is just like in the movies to the actual life that unravels in front of her. In this coming of age story, she struggles with understanding herself, the changing world, educational pressures, bullying, competition over marks  - all of it wrapped up in a transcending journey of first love.

Widower Jay Singh, a US-based physician, loses his memory during an accident while visiting India, his homeland. But as his memory begins to return, things come to light which throws doubt on his memory and the accident itself. Soon everybody, including Jay, begins to ask a question - Did Jay kill his wife?

Virtual Reality (VR) Planetarium - Travel back to the beginning of time and experience the birth of the sun. Discover how it came to support life, how it threatens life and how its energy will one day fade away.

The Incredible Sun is a English 7D Virtual Reality (VR) Planetarium - Discover our star through the breathtaking timelapses. Thanks to the real images taken by the Solar Dynamics Observatory and processed by advanced mathematical methods, you will experience the true nature of the Sun and find out that it is far from being as calm as it seems at first glance
